## SMALL DESCRIPTION ABOUNT THE NEW MAC M1


Mac m1 is the first soc(system on chip) designed by apple based on ARM architecture  
It is the worlds first 5nm cpu in a main stream lapotop


![MAC M1](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

## WHAT IS A SOC


It is an integrated circuit which consits of most of the parts of the computer i.e CPU,MEMORY,STORAGE,INPUT, OUTPUT ETC

![SOC](https://www.apple.com/v/mac/m1/a/images/overview/chip_memory__dnhm4hh2i7ma_large_2x.jpg)

## WHAT IS SPECIALITY OF M1

It is an octa core cpu based on a 5nm process which helps in efficiency and apple claims it has the best battery life of laptops and the fastest chip in any category of laptops  

This 5nm design has helped apple to include a integrated gpu and neural engine and apple claims that the integrated gpu is the fastest integrated gpu on a personal computer which is capable of executing nearly 25,000 threads at a time  

![GPU ](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
